# MCP / Cursor discipline (ongoing)

- Prefer **one coherent fix** per incident; don’t ask for endless restarts.
- **`bored`** stays aligned with prod **`https://bored.desync.link`** unless the user explicitly directs otherwise (see **`kanban-card-workflow.mdc`**).
